28:16.057 --> 28:17.352
- Okay.

28:17.353 --> 28:20.052
- Do you want me to stay a little longer?

28:20.053 --> 28:22.275
- Nah, nah, you can go.

28:22.276 --> 28:23.529
- Oh, I can go?
- Yeah.

28:23.530 --> 28:24.363
- You're a big man,

28:24.364 --> 28:26.149
