28:26.150 --> 28:27.263
- Yeah.
- Okay.

28:32.526 --> 28:33.526
Well.

28:40.730 --> 28:42.689
Do I look okay?
- You look fine.

28:44.060 --> 28:47.502
- Ooh, I love you.
