28:47.503 --> 28:50.243
- There's a little somethin' on your face.

28:52.010 --> 28:53.158
Got it.

28:53.159 --> 28:55.189
Okay, have a nice night.

28:55.190 --> 28:56.190
- You too.

30:50.638 --> 30:53.358
- The country, it
doesn't mean anything.

31:30.394 --> 31:32.313
- Owen!

31:33.783 --> 31:34.783
Ah!
- Oh!

31:38.540 --> 31:39.540
Who are you?

31:40.696 --> 31:42.236
- Who are you?

31:42.237 --> 31:44.890
