31:45.735 --> 31:47.902
- You're looking for Owen.

31:50.634 --> 31:51.634
All right.

31:53.318 --> 31:54.929
Makes sense.

31:54.930 --> 31:55.930
Oh, wow.

31:56.918 --> 31:59.474
Okay.

31:59.475 --> 32:01.058
- Wait, wait, wait.

32:01.986 --> 32:03.829
- Oh, no, no, no, no, no.

32:03.830 --> 32:04.670
