32:11.085 --> 32:14.069
Yeah, do I look 18 to you?

32:14.070 --> 32:17.386
- Maybe Owen likes older women.

32:17.387 --> 32:19.943
- Have more
confidence, sweetie.

32:21.050 --> 32:24.759
